 plc added “our reading and london office put us in the perfect place for this deal considering reading and the surrounding areas are referred to as the tech capital for the uk we are delighted to have been able to support lms capital and hope to work with them again” coretx holdings is an aimlisted it managed services provider focused on the uk midmarket gateley plc’s corporate team is one of the largest national teams in the uk and consistently advises on more transactions than other advisors in the market share share email facebook linkedin twitter google pinterest news navigationblogsbriefingslatest newsupcoming eventstag cloudacquisition appointment aquisition awards banking banking  finance birmingham charity charles glaskie construction corporate ctm east midlands employment entrepreneurial floating fundraise gateley gateley plc hire investment law leeds legal leicester leigh whittaker london london stock exchange manchester mark rutherford nottingham partner paul simpson private equity reading real estate richard clitherow stock tax thames valley tom durrant uk victoria elliot yorkshire zum mohammed other articlesjulgateley plc advises city football group on north american joint venturejulgateley plc provides pro bono advice to iraqi refugee charityjungateley plc announces  promotions across national networkjungateley plc expands private client offering in the east midlandsmaygateley plc takes on  mile national cycle sportive for help for heroes gateleyplc gateleyplcfollow us twitterthe ‘fresh voice’ of uk financial trade httpstcohkpzfqjast july  reply retweet favoritetwitterrt baby lifeline babylifeline we are delighted to present bwhnhs and heartofengland with new maternity monitoring equipment with money raised… httpstcoqpxbikzozst july  reply retweet favorite latest newsview all julgateley plc advises city football group on north american joint venturegateley plc the legal business of lawled professional services group gateley read more about gateley plc